name: So Ill Clippers
description: Along with crazy glue, tape, brushes, liquid chalk and various good-luck charms, nail clippers are an essential component of a climber's kit. Includes 2 different sizes of clippers for perfectly manicured sending.Made of stainless steel with precision-ground edges.2 sizes for fingers and toes.Thumb pads are comfy to use with shredded tips.Built-in nail catcher won't spread trimmings around the gym or crag.Bright green handles are easy to find in the bottom of your chalk bucket.
